request.description:
Triggers the IDS generation flow. The assistant will call `start_ids_generation`, then search APIHub for each mentioned API, produce the full IDS document, call `save_generated_file`, and embed a download link in its final reply.

The tool pills visible in the SSE stream:
  tool.started   {name: start_ids_generation}
  tool.started   {name: search_rest_api_operations}  (repeated per API lookup)
  tool.started   {name: get_rest_api_operations_specification}
  tool.started   {name: save_generated_file}
  tool.completed {name: save_generated_file}

The final `message.assistant.completed` contains a markdown link of the form `[IDS_TCS.md](/api/v1/generated-files/<id>?token=<jwt>)`.

